\par\par \b \uc2 Central banker in graft case   \b0\par\par\uc2 747 \uc2 words\par \uc2 31 January 2008\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 6\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2008 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The Corruption Eradication Commission's (KPK) naming of \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  governor Burhanuddin Abdullah and two other senior executives of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  as suspects in a Rp 31.5 billion (US$3.38 million) corruption case should be welcomed as more evidence of the government's determination to fight malfeasance.   \par \par \uc2 The market and the general \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  should not be inordinately worried that the legal move by the corruption buster will adversely affect the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 's ability to exercise its function as the bedrock of the monetary system, the guardian of monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and the arbitrator of the financial system.   \par \par \uc2 It is indeed unfortunate that this scandal should hit \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  at a time when better cooperation and coordination between the \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  and monetary authorities are badly needed in coping with the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the global financial market and \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  had faced a much more serious problem under a much worse \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and political situation when its then governor Sjahril Sabirin was jailed for six months in the second half of 2000 and was eventually sentenced by the Central Jakarta District Court to three years in jail.   \par \par \uc2 But it was still business as usual at the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 . Its board of governors worked normally. Sjahril resumed his job as soon as he was released from prosecutors' detention in December 2000. He even retained his position and continued working normally after his conviction in March 2002 while his appeal process was underway. The Jakarta High Court acquitted Sjahril of all charges in August 2002 and he served his term fully until June 2003.   \par \par \uc2 We hope that Burhanuddin also will get similar legal treatment. There is no strong reason for the KPK to put him in custody pending his investigation and eventual prosecution and trial proceedings.   \par \par \uc2 We are confident that Burhanuddin, supported by the members of the board of governors, including senior deputy governor Miranda Goeltom, will still be able to discharge his tasks effectively until the end of his term in June. And judging from the millions of dollars \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  has so generously given away in legal fees to its former governors and deputy governors who faced corruption charges, Burhanuddin can also rest assured that he will be defended by a team of the best lawyers in the country.   \par \par \uc2 The most immediate adverse impact could be on Burhanuddin's chances of being reappointed by the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  for a second term. President Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono should nominate to the House three candidates for the new governor before the end of next month at the latest for selection by the House in May and Burhanuddin, given his case now, might not be included among the nominees.   \par \par \uc2 Burhanuddin flatly denied any wrongdoing on Tuesday, asserting that the decision to allocate Rp 31.5 billion for building \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  opinion in favor of \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  regarding the proposed amendments to the 1999 \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law was a collective decision of the board of governors.   \par \par \uc2 However, \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 's decisions in March and July 2003 to allocate Rp 68.5 billion in legal fees to its former governor Soedradjad Djiwandono and four former deputy governors who faced corruption charges and Rp 31.5 billion for a \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2 -opinion campaign related to the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  law amendments raised a lot of questions.   \par \par \uc2 After all, \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  had just emerged from technical bankruptcy due to its big losses in coping with the banking crisis in 1997-1999.   \par \par \uc2 A twist to the corruption allegations against Burhanuddin and two other lower-echelon officials of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  is that the irregularities in the accounts of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 's Indonesian Banking Development Foundation were discovered by the Supreme Audit Agency.   \par \par \uc2 It was the agency's chairman, Anwar Nasution, who reported the graft case to the KPK last year. Nasution was \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 's senior deputy governor when the board of governors decided on the disbursement of the funds, which according to preliminary investigations, flowed to several members of the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 Despite his status as a suspect and eventually a defendant, Burhanuddin still deserves the treatment accorded to the governor of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  until the court proves him guilty.   \par \par \uc2 We should let the KPK and the corruption court decide on the case, hopefully with high expediency. Because unlike central banks in many other countries, the law assigns \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  the multiple tasks of maintaining the stability of the rupiah, controlling inflation and supervising the banking industry.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020080131e41v0000k\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
