\par\par \b \uc2 Kadin slams audit agency's demand for more power   \b0\par\par\uc2 Agustina Wayansari , The Jakarta Post, Jakarta   \par \uc2 433 \uc2 words\par \uc2 19 February 2008\par \uc2 The Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par 14\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2008 The Jakarta Post   \par \par \uc2 The Indonesian Chamber of Commerce and Industry (Kadin) announced Monday its opposition to the Supreme Audit Agency's (BPK) demand for greater authority in probing the state's \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue.   \par \par \uc2 The BPK is currently in court for a judicial review on the law on general rules and procedures of \b \highlight22\uc2 taxation\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 The agency is particularly adamant about scrapping an article in the law that requires the agency to obtain written permission from the finance minister to obtain detailed information on the government's \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenue.   \par \par \uc2 Kadin deputy chairman for \b \highlight22\uc2 public policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , \b \highlight22\uc2 taxation\b0 \highlight\uc2  and customs Hariyadi B. Sukamdani said a greater BPK authority would mean an infringement on taxpayers' right to keep their information confidential, as protected by law.   \par \par \uc2 "We cannot accept the agency's request to access all data on state \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  revenues that include taxpayer records. The BPK will not be able to guarantee the taxpayers' right to secrecy.   \par \par \uc2 "Such authority would have a negative impact on us, business players, as we are also taxpayers," Hariyadi said.   \par \par \uc2 Earlier, the BPK chairman told a panel of judges in the first hearing session on Feb. 5 that greater authority was necessary to boost the agency's capacity in probing corruption cases.   \par \par \uc2 He said according to the law on the inspection of state financial accountability and management, the agency was allowed full access to all data, information and documents necessary for inspecting the financial affairs of the government.   \par \par \uc2 Hariyadi said a representative from Kadin would stand as witness in the judicial court session Tuesday, presenting a formal argument to counter the BPK's request.   \par \par \uc2 He further said the existing laws and regulations on \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  already accommodated the BPK's needs and that it was normal to require formal approval from the minister for certain information.   \par \par \uc2 Kadin \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  committee chairman Prijohandojo Kristanto said the BPK's request would also discourage potential investors who remain unsure of the current \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2 .   \par \par \uc2 "Our investment sector hasn't recovered from the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  crisis a decade ago and this new \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2  will hamper potential investors who in fact are still \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  of the current \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," said Prijohandojo.   \par \par \uc2 Bambang Soesatyo, who chairs the \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  and monetary committee at Kadin, said the access to confidential information was also not good for business as competitors could also enjoy access to any information made \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  by the BPK.   \par \par \uc2 "We're not against transparency or clean governance, but making private information \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  will give our competitors free access to our confidential data to learn about the company's business strategy", he said.   \par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020080219e42j0001a\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
