id a financial crunch.\par \par \uc2 Political \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  expert Makmur Keliat said President Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono should explain to the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  the implications of the suspension of the Indonesia Stock Exchange (IDX) and the role of the \uc2 Bakrie Group\uc2  in the suspension decision.\par \par \uc2 "Many are wondering what is really happening. This is the kind of incident that could wipe out \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  trust in authorities and business. So the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  needs to get a logical explanation," he said.\par \par \uc2 In addition to the regional trend of falling share prices, many have suggested another factor behind the Jakarta market's free fall from Monday to Wednesday last week was that speculation over PT \uc2 Bakrie & Brothers\uc2  and its units dragged down the group's shares.\par \par \uc2 The decline in stock prices of Bakrie and its units, in particular PT Bumi Resources, was the main driver behind the IDX's 10.03 percent fall last Monday, with transactions involving the group making up around a third of the total transactions.\par \par \uc2 The speculations center on concerns Bakrie will not be able to pay its short-term debts, which amount to US$1.43 billion. The loans are backed by the shares of affiliated companies, including Bumi, \uc2 PT Energi Mega Persada\uc2  and PT Bakrie Sumatra Plantations.\par \par \uc2 Makmur said the suspension send the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  a strong signal that the financial crisis was politicized, given that the \uc2 Bakrie Group\uc2  is linked to Aburizal Bakrie, Yudhoyono's coordinating minister for the people's welfare.\par \par \uc2 "Politics begins to play a part here and it creates \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," Makmur said.\par \par \uc2 "The government must be transparent about what companies here have been hit by the bankruptcy of U.S. financial firms. We need to know if the tentacles of the financial trouble are reaching to Indonesian firms to protect the \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2 ."\par \par \uc2 Lawmaker Ganjar Parnowo of the Indonesian Democratic Party of Struggle (PDI-P) promised his party would not stand in the way of any government efforts to soften the crisis as long as the policies made sense.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020081013e4ad00006\par }\par \b \uc2 Search Summary\b0\par \par  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx2000\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx9072\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Text\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \li50\uc2 (economic or economy) and (uncertain or uncertainty or uncertainties) and (policy or public or tax or taxation or taxes or taxed or spending or expenditure or fiscal or stimulus or budget or deficit or national debt or tariff or subsidies or subsidy or Bank Indonesia or central bank or reserves or interest rates or fiscal or legislation or legislative or house of representatives or regulation)\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx2000\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx9072\row } \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx2000\clvertalt\clbrdrt\brdrs\clbrdrl\brdrs\clbrdrb\brdrs\clbrdrr\brdrs \cellx9072\pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Date\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \li50\uc2 All Dates\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {